## 7. Risks and Unresolved Questions

### Identified Risks

| Risk                                                                                                                                                                   | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation                                                                                                                     |
| ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------- | ------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **`Effect.Service` generic method signatures** — methods like `load(path: string, level?: number): Effect<SoulManifest, SoulLoadError>` may have typing issues         | Medium     | High   | Have fallback to `Context.Tag` pattern if `Effect.Service` has issues with generic return types                                |
