| **`pi.sendMessage` inside Effect context** — `/soul` calls `pi.sendMessage` which is imperative                                                                        | High       | Medium | Wrap via `Effect.sync(() => { pi.sendMessage(...); return; })` for simple calls, or pass `pi` reference to imperative handlers |
