2. **`NodeRuntime.runMain` vs `ManagedRuntime`** — confirm `ManagedRuntime` is the correct pattern for Pi extensions
3. **`import { NodeFileSystem } from "@effect/platform-node"`** — verify exact export path in v0.96.x
