### `resources_discover` — `src/events.ts:47-64`

**Prompt paths order** — **Confirmed regression:**

| Order | Reference                     | New code                                 |
| ----- | ----------------------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| 1st   | `.pi/souls`                   | `~/.pi/agent/souls` (expanded)           |
| 2nd   | `./souls`                     | `~/.openclaw/souls/clawsouls` (expanded) |
